</p>
<ul>
    <li>jQuery 2.2.0 <sub>(<a href="https://github.com/jquery/jquery/tree/2.2.0" rel="noopener noreferrer" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" target="_blank">source</a>, <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jquery/jquery/2.2.0/LICENSE.txt" rel="noopener noreferrer" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" target="_blank">license</a>)</sub></li>
    <li>jQuery Validate 1.14.0 <sub>(<a href="https://github.com/jquery-validation/jquery-validation/tree/1.14.0" rel="noopener noreferrer" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" target="_blank">source</a>, <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jquery-validation/jquery-validation/1.14.0/LICENSE.md" rel="noopener noreferrer" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" target="_blank">license</a>)</sub></li>
    <li>jQuery Validate Unobtrusive 3.2.6 <sub>(<a href="https://github.com/aspnet/jquery-validation-unobtrusive/tree/v3.2.6" rel="noopener noreferrer" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" target="_blank">source</a>, <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aspnet/jquery-validation-unobtrusive/v3.2.6/LICENSE.txt" rel="noopener noreferrer" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" target="_blank">license</a>)</sub></li>
