    using Subresource Integrity (SRI). All third-party links, images,
    stylesheets and scripts are configured with a Referrer Policy of
    "no-referrer".
<p>
    subscriptiond automatically deletes:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Lists that have not been accessed within @Constants.ListMaxAgeMin.Humanize().</li>
    <li>Metadata for videos published earlier than @Constants.VideoMaxAge.Humanize() ago.</li>
</ul>

